@startuml
title IKEv2 Negotiation: IKE SA then IPsec SA (CHILD_SA)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FDEEEE
  ParticipantBorderColor #B54A4A
  LifeLineBorderColor #B54A4A
  ArrowColor #B54A4A
}
participant "Initiator" as I
participant "Responder" as R

== IKE_SA_INIT (establish the IKE SA) ==
I -> R : SA proposals, DH key share, nonce
R --> I : chosen SA, DH key share, nonce
note over I, R : Shared secret derived; IKE SA now protects further signaling

== IKE_AUTH (authenticate peers + first IPsec SA) ==
I -> R : identity, AUTH, CHILD_SA proposal, traffic selectors
R --> I : identity, AUTH, chosen CHILD_SA, traffic selectors
note over I, R : Peers authenticated (cert / PSK / EAP); IPsec SA (CHILD_SA) established

== Protected data traffic ==
I <-> R : ESP-protected packets over the IPsec SA
@enduml
